screen_desc: A mobile screen displaying an online shopping app. The top section has a search bar with a microphone icon and a QR code scanner icon. Below it, there is a banner titled "Beauty essentials" with images of beauty products. Three sections are highlighted: "Keep shopping for Laptop stands," "Recommended deal for you," and "Glow up under $25." At the bottom, a pop-up message encourages users to "Shop faster with voice" with a yellow button labeled "Turn on microphone." Additional information about voice shopping and privacy is provided, along with a link to permissions settings.

ui_elements.text: Your audio is transcribed in the cloud then automatically deleted. We store and use the transcripts as described in our Privacy Notice. Learn more about shopping with voice.
